10
00:00:40,670 --> 00:00:42,040
Double the price

11
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:47,250
No problem. I'll arrange it right away.

12
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:49,040
Please, have a seat. This way.

13
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:08,380
Lily

14
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:17,500
I'm sorry, Miss Sun

15
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:21,039
