16
00:01:21,710 --> 00:01:24,380
Who dares to take my guy?

17
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:36,380
Handsome guy here for male companions too?

18
00:01:36,380 --> 00:01:38,289
Come on, Tony

19
00:01:38,289 --> 00:01:41,789
Rourou came to see me first

20
00:01:41,789 --> 00:01:43,500
Who knows what kind of luck you're having,

21
