22
00:01:46,580 --> 00:01:49,170
Double?

23
00:01:49,170 --> 00:01:49,960
Since when

24
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:53,289
did my face become that valuable?

25
00:01:55,130 --> 00:01:58,330
Miss Sun, I'm truly sorry.

26
00:01:58,330 --> 00:02:01,330
It's fine, since it's a guy,

27
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:04,380
I won't make a fuss. Go ahead.

28
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:06,000
But I don't want to

29
