After my shift—

30
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,630
Alright, don't keep the guest waiting.

31
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,000
I'll make it up to you later

32
00:02:17,579 --> 00:02:19,540
Hello, I'm Jay.

33
00:02:20,579 --> 00:02:22,630
