34
00:02:39,579 --> 00:02:41,040
Hello

35
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:49,670
David

36
00:02:50,670 --> 00:02:51,750
Hi, David

37
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:57,460
Miss Sun, I'm really sorry.

38
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:59,170
Actually, other hosts in our club

39
00:02:59,170 --> 00:03:00,130
are excellent too

40
00:03:00,130 --> 00:03:01,790
Maybe you'd like to try someone else?

41
00:03:01,790 --> 00:03:04,670
Tony, don't worry about me

42
00:03:04,670 --> 00:03:06,000
I'll manage

43
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,420
David

44
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:15,920
it's your first time here, right?

45
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:20,420
Come, let's have a drink first.

46
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:26,250
Ah-Jie

47
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,420
Sorry, it's Jay

48
00:03:30,420 --> 00:03:32,630
J-A-Y

49
