63
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,670
According to my dental appraisal,

64
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:37,130
the diamonds are real.

65
00:04:39,670 --> 00:04:42,420
Even he knows about Pan Hao's diamonds?

66
00:04:43,670 --> 00:04:44,500
If you don't know

67
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:46,170
how to spend all that money,

68
00:04:46,170 --> 00:04:49,170
invest in me setting up another Men's Club.

69
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:54,040
How did you know about the diamonds?

70
00:04:55,250 --> 00:04:57,250
This morning, one of our guys, Ah-Jun,

71
00:04:57,250 --> 00:04:59,170
tried to swipe Pan Hao's diamonds

72
00:04:59,170 --> 00:05:00,380
but got caught red-handed.

73
00:05:04,330 --> 00:05:06,210
Pan Hao kept it from us all this time

74
00:05:06,210 --> 00:05:09,000
without a single hint

75
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,670
Not cool at all.

76
00:05:10,670 --> 00:05:12,960
Hunter, stop slacking off.

77
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:15,080
