78
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,170
Copied that

79
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,170
Hey, friend

80
00:05:18,170 --> 00:05:19,170
Don't forget about me

81
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,790
Someone else is after his diamonds too

82
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:55,170
What is it?

83
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:58,790
