94
00:06:21,130 --> 00:06:22,420
I see

95
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,580
Sun Rourou just called

96
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:01,330
a guy named Ah-Jun

97
00:07:01,330 --> 00:07:03,290
at the club

98
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,880
was trying to steal Pan Hao's diamonds

99
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,670
Can’t even pull off a simple job—

100
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:15,250
and got caught

101
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:26,040
So… you sent the guy?

102
00:07:31,290 --> 00:07:34,630
He owes me a lot of money

103
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:38,000
and you haven’t made any progress,

104
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:42,290
I figured more hands would speed things up.

105
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:52,000
Now, you're saying I'm incompetent

106
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:55,380
or planning to keep the diamonds yourself?

107
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:56,790
