108
00:07:58,170 --> 00:07:59,630
Come on

109
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:05,290
I wanted to surprise you

110
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:07,170
after I got the diamonds

111
00:08:10,960 --> 00:08:12,920
what's with

112
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,920
