116
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,540
Ah-Jie

117
00:09:18,880 --> 00:09:20,420
Sorry

118
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,790
I'm sorry

119
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:28,460
I failed to protect you

120
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:29,540
I'm sorry

121
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:31,750
You did well.

122
00:09:34,130 --> 00:09:35,670
Everything is okay

123
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:37,710
Sorry

124
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:39,330
It's okay

125
00:09:39,330 --> 00:09:41,750
I'm sorry

126
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:46,830
It's okay

127
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,170
Excuse me

128
00:09:48,170 --> 00:09:50,670
Is Jay not taking good care of you?

129
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:53,290
