130
00:09:53,290 --> 00:09:55,670
No—don’t replace him.

131
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:57,130
He's excellent

132
00:09:57,130 --> 00:09:59,250
Please don’t replace him.

133
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:05,330
Alright, sorry for the interruption

134
00:10:05,330 --> 00:10:08,000
let me know if you need anything

135
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:15,420
hey, I'm not going anywhere

136
00:10:18,130 --> 00:10:21,130
why don't you wipe...

137
00:10:21,130 --> 00:10:22,500
your tears first?

138
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:37,380
Sorry—

139
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:39,290
I lost my composure.

140
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:41,330
No worries

141
00:10:41,330 --> 00:10:42,630
If something’s bothering you,

142
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,960
