156
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:40,040
No

157
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:43,290
David, No

158
00:11:43,290 --> 00:11:45,210
David No

159
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,290
Not David

160
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:47,380
No

161
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,880
David  No

162
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,630
David

163
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:52,330
No

164
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:53,210
David, No

165
00:11:53,210 --> 00:11:55,420
I know what you're thinking

166
00:11:57,130 --> 00:11:59,290
Not that kind of “casting couch” sacrifice.

167
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,290
We're shooting a BL drama

168
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:23,880
A lot of actors avoid this genre now.

169
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:26,460
But I'm straight. I like women.

170
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:28,580
The character starts out straight too.

171
00:12:28,580 --> 00:12:30,830
But then he falls in love

172
00:12:30,830 --> 00:12:32,130
and gender stops mattering.

173
00:12:35,920 --> 00:12:38,170
Take your time thinking about it.

174
00:12:38,170 --> 00:12:41,080
The series will be filmed in Thailand.

175
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,210
If you're in,

176
00:12:42,210 --> 00:12:43,330
we'll bring the main cast over for training.

177
00:12:43,330 --> 00:12:45,420
next month

178
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:47,960
Just let us know before the end of the month.

179
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,540
Thailand...

180
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,750
I own a private island

181
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,830
in Thailand

182
00:12:54,830 --> 00:12:57,380
Most of the scenes will be shot there

183
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:59,540
The environment is amazing

184
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:01,790
The ocean view is unbeatable

185
00:13:01,790 --> 00:13:04,420
After filming, if you'd like,

186
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,330
you can stay there

187
00:13:05,330 --> 00:13:06,710
as long as you want.

188
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,170
Totally up to you

189
00:13:09,170 --> 00:13:12,830
If I go to Thailand…

190
00:13:12,830 --> 00:13:14,630
Chiang won't be able to find me.

191
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:18,540
But what about Rourou?

192
00:13:22,170 --> 00:13:23,710
Think it over.

193
00:13:23,710 --> 00:13:25,920
I'll wait for you answer

194
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:27,920
It's fine, I've got it.

195
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,130
I'll be waiting

196
00:13:51,880 --> 00:13:54,080
Careful, David. steps here

197
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,790
Here

198
00:13:55,790 --> 00:13:56,630
Another one.

199
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,040
There

200
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,380
See you tomorrow

201
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:11,420
Sure, see you tomorrow.

202
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,290
Bye

203
00:14:13,290 --> 00:14:14,920
Bye, David

204
00:14:26,330 --> 00:14:27,880
