205
00:14:30,130 --> 00:14:32,130
Earsdropping on my conversation with a guest?

206
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:33,420
Trying to steal my client?

207
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:37,750
Honestly, going to Thailand might be good for you.

208
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,920
