211
00:14:44,630 --> 00:14:46,750
True

212
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:48,080
I think so

213
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:51,290
Staying in the club is like sitting on a time bomb.

214
00:14:53,710 --> 00:14:58,170
One day it might just blow up

215
00:14:58,170 --> 00:14:59,540
and drag you guys down with me.

216
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:02,500
It's just...

217
00:15:05,540 --> 00:15:07,250
Can't let go of Sun Rourou?

218
00:15:10,460 --> 00:15:13,580
You're barely keeping yourself afloat.

219
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:15,040
Take care of yourself first.

220
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:19,460
Also,

221
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:21,250
there are a lot of scams lately,

222
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:22,710
you've never acted before,

223
00:15:22,710 --> 00:15:25,000
Why would someone cast you as a lead?

224
00:15:26,290 --> 00:15:30,130
But after thinking it over carefully…

225
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:31,290
the way David

226
00:15:31,290 --> 00:15:33,710
looked at me…

227
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:36,250
