228
00:15:38,250 --> 00:15:41,830
Should I book you a neurologist or an eye doctor?

229
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,380
You look handsome to me - What doctor do I need?

230
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,630
Now, you're pretty normal

231
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:49,920
hey

232
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:54,540
YuChuan

233
00:15:54,540 --> 00:15:56,540
Can I use your car?

234
