What for?

235
00:15:57,830 --> 00:15:59,330
Don't ask questions now

236
00:15:59,330 --> 00:16:00,540
Just lend it to me first

237
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:02,210
and cover for me.

238
00:16:02,210 --> 00:16:03,420
Don't let Tony know

239
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:05,290
I'm sneaking out.

240
00:16:05,290 --> 00:16:06,920
cover what?

241
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,790
Where are you going?

242
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,710
Meeting a friend.

243
00:16:20,710 --> 00:16:22,040
for late night snack

244
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:27,790
You're going to see Sun Rourou, aren't you?

245
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:34,420
Seriously?

246
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:37,210
You're already catching feelings?

247
00:16:37,210 --> 00:16:41,750
Tony, it's my first love,

248
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:43,790
hard to resist.

249
00:16:45,710 --> 00:16:47,250
First love or not,

250
00:16:47,250 --> 00:16:49,080
it's been years,

251
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:51,290
how do you know she hasn't changed

252
00:16:51,290 --> 00:16:54,170
that she's still the same person?

253
00:16:57,040 --> 00:17:00,460
Don't let love fool you

254
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:04,500
Even love loses value over time.

255
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:05,790
Wake up

256
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,630
Tony

257
00:17:08,630 --> 00:17:10,829
Rourou is really innocent

258
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:12,829
and she's good to me.

259
00:17:12,829 --> 00:17:14,380
So,

260
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,460
could you cut me some slack?

261
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:19,210
Let me experience

262
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:21,000
what love feels like.

263
00:17:24,170 --> 00:17:26,250
Fine. Since you handled

264
00:17:26,250 --> 00:17:29,210
David so well earlier

265
00:17:29,210 --> 00:17:29,830
go ahead.

266
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:31,040
Yes

267
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:36,880
Tony

268
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:03,080
Zhen, your cooking is amazing.

269
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:04,710
One sip of this chicken soup

270
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:06,750
