275
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:22,040
Too bad the mastermind Leo escaped.

276
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:23,380
That guy is disgusting.

277
00:18:23,380 --> 00:18:24,790
He scammed so many girls

278
00:18:24,790 --> 00:18:26,580
and just walked away.

279
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:28,290
What a coward.

280
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,540
With things like this,

281
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:33,960
