282
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:37,210
Someone lies, someone chooses to believe

283
00:18:37,210 --> 00:18:38,790
You can't control that.

284
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,750
But...

285
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:47,250
We can't just do nothing.

286
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:48,460
Of course not.

287
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:49,670
But some things

288
00:18:49,670 --> 00:18:52,080
aren't yours to fix.

289
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:53,710
I've always believed

290
00:18:53,710 --> 00:18:55,500
everything happens for a reason.

291
00:18:58,080 --> 00:19:01,170
So meeting you was fate too?

292
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:02,420
Can you not use

293
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:04,130
