294
00:19:04,130 --> 00:19:05,630
I'm serious.

295
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:08,790
Speaking of which,

296
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:10,540
is your compulsive behavioral disorder thing—

297
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:11,750
getting any better?

298
00:19:12,580 --> 00:19:17,130
Much better than before.

299
00:19:18,710 --> 00:19:19,380
Must be because of you.

300
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:20,920
You're always here with me.

301
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,080
You're such a smooth talker.

302
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:25,130
Go shower. I'm going to bed.

303
00:19:25,130 --> 00:19:26,040
So early?

304
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:27,750
No more chatting?

305
00:19:28,670 --> 00:19:31,000
Go already

306
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,130
Pan Hao

307
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:16,250
There's something I want to ask you.

308
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:19,540
What is it? Go ahead.

309
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:35,290
Are you hiding something from me?

310
00:21:36,290 --> 00:21:38,460
A secret?

311
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:40,330
No

312
00:21:40,330 --> 00:21:43,210
Besides,

313
00:21:43,210 --> 00:21:45,830
I always tell you what happens with my clients.

314
00:21:45,830 --> 00:21:47,960
Why would you ask?

315
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:51,580
Yesterday,at the club,

316
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:55,540
Chang Yihao told me that you're a diamond millionaire.

317
00:21:55,540 --> 00:21:59,290
That bigmouth…

318
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:03,210
Baby, I wanted to tell you

319
00:22:03,210 --> 00:22:04,460
I just couldn't find

320
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:07,170
the right time.

321
00:22:07,170 --> 00:22:11,080
If someone suddenly gets that much money,

322
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:13,880
people would think it's suspicious.

323
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:17,080
I was afraid you'd think I'm dangerous

324
00:22:17,080 --> 00:22:19,210
that you'd stay away from me.

325
00:22:19,210 --> 00:22:20,920
Is that so?

326
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,920
I thought you were just playing with me

327
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:27,500
for not telling me.

328
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:29,130
Of course not.

329
00:22:29,130 --> 00:22:32,040
I've liked you since high school.

330
00:22:32,040 --> 00:22:33,710
I swear to god

331
00:22:33,710 --> 00:22:36,210
My feelings for Sun Rourou

332
00:22:36,210 --> 00:22:38,250
are completely genuine.

333
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:40,540
may I get hit by a car, if I'm lying

334
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:44,500
Then I should buy you more accidental insurance

335
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:47,790
so your death would be worth more.

336
00:22:50,210 --> 00:22:53,420
huh, you only want my money

337
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:55,420
not me

338
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:59,670
I'm just teasing you.

339
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:04,540
So where did the diamonds come from?

340
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,880
I stole them.

341
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,130
You stole them?

342
00:23:13,830 --> 00:23:15,750
No wonder whenever we go out

343
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:17,920
