344
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:20,750
You should've told me earlier,

345
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:21,540
I wouldn't have

346
00:23:21,540 --> 00:23:23,420
asked you to meet outside.

347
00:23:26,170 --> 00:23:26,710
I also heard

348
00:23:26,710 --> 00:23:31,330
