353
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,630
No...

354
00:23:42,630 --> 00:23:44,630
That's too conspicuous.

355
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:45,920
Or...

356
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:50,460
How about this—

357
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:52,710
the safe we bought,

358
00:23:52,710 --> 00:23:54,920
let's keep it at your place

359
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:57,380
