361
00:24:02,580 --> 00:24:03,920
What do you think?

362
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:09,460
Do you really think that's okay?

363
00:24:09,460 --> 00:24:13,500
What if I sell your diamonds?

364
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:17,670
I trust you wouldn't do that to me.

365
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:44,170
baby

366
00:24:44,170 --> 00:24:48,880
One day, if I wanted to take you away from here,

367
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:50,790
would you come with me?

368
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:53,750
why?

369
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:58,540
Planning to hide on a deserted island?

370
00:25:01,580 --> 00:25:04,670
Those diamonds are stolen after all.

371
00:25:04,670 --> 00:25:08,130
I can't hide forever.

372
00:25:08,130 --> 00:25:10,040
I need to find a chance

373
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:12,250
to lay low somewhere else.

374
00:25:15,380 --> 00:25:17,710
Do you even need to ask?

375
00:25:17,710 --> 00:25:19,540
I've already given myself to you.

376
00:25:19,540 --> 00:25:21,750
Wherever you go, I'll go.

377
00:25:25,540 --> 00:25:28,130
About that safe—

378
00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:29,250
I've already ordered it

379
00:25:29,250 --> 00:25:32,080
which should arrive in a couple of days.

380
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:33,210
So fast!

381
00:25:33,210 --> 00:25:34,380
Otherwise,

382
00:25:34,380 --> 00:25:37,790
