386
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:47,710
See? I'm smart.

387
00:25:47,710 --> 00:25:51,290
Fine. You're so smart, we'll do it your way.

388
00:25:51,290 --> 00:25:53,670
So, can I

389
00:25:53,670 --> 00:25:56,250
