394
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:11,420
Of course

395
00:26:13,250 --> 00:26:15,290
Don't worry

396
00:26:22,580 --> 00:26:25,380
You should get to work

397
00:26:25,380 --> 00:26:26,420
