403
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:36,790
Stealing the diamonds should be easy.

404
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:38,290
How did you mess it up?

405
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:45,790
Talk

406
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:47,630
B-Biao…

407
00:27:47,630 --> 00:27:53,040
