421
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,080
Seriously

422
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:39,080
I know how

423
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:41,540
How?

424
00:28:41,540 --> 00:28:43,790
Let me tell you

425
00:28:47,710 --> 00:28:50,630
