426
00:28:50,630 --> 00:28:53,210
Pan Hao will hand over the diamonds.

427
00:28:53,210 --> 00:28:55,000
Just give me some more time.

428
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,380
Please, Biao

429
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:57,670
Please...

430
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:05,880
I'm giving you one last chance.

431
00:29:10,790 --> 00:29:12,670
Very last time

432
00:29:18,210 --> 00:29:19,670
Thank you

433
00:29:19,670 --> 00:29:21,130
Thanks, Biao

434
00:29:38,420 --> 00:29:40,670
Didn't expect you to ask me out.

435
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,960
I wanted to talk about

436
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:47,330
