466
00:31:21,710 --> 00:31:25,250
I saw her at the club that night.

467
00:31:25,250 --> 00:31:26,670
She's pretty.

468
00:31:26,670 --> 00:31:29,170
Very pretty.

469
00:31:29,170 --> 00:31:31,540
I'm open-minded

470
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:34,630
I don't care if you're seeing someone.

471
00:31:34,630 --> 00:31:36,790
I like you

472
00:31:36,790 --> 00:31:38,790
