OK

591
00:38:30,580 --> 00:38:31,580
Bonuses are done.

592
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:33,250
Back to work

593
00:38:33,250 --> 00:38:36,250
Pan Hao, even if you're leaving,

594
00:38:36,250 --> 00:38:38,960
do your job while you're here.

595
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:40,670
You still have to work hard

596
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,750
Yes sir!

597
00:38:41,750 --> 00:38:43,250
all right

598
00:38:43,250 --> 00:38:44,830
let's get it

599
00:38:44,830 --> 00:38:46,170
ACE

600
00:38:48,330 --> 00:38:51,130
A day's work for a day's pay.

601
00:38:51,130 --> 00:38:52,420
Yu Chuan

602
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:56,920
These guys of yours here…

603
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:59,670
do you really know their backgrounds?

604
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:11,210
Well...

605
00:39:11,210 --> 00:39:13,790
I don't even fully know

606
00:39:13,790 --> 00:39:15,670
my own uncle's background.

607
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:44,960
What is it?

608
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:48,540
Chiang knows Pan Hao is hiding here.

609
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,750
Are you sure?

610
00:39:49,750 --> 00:39:50,580
Yes

611
00:39:50,580 --> 00:39:52,500
He called Ma Cheng-en this afternoon

612
00:39:52,500 --> 00:39:53,880
and told him to deal with it.

613
00:40:00,580 --> 00:40:01,420
Got it.

614
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,790
You can go.

615
00:40:27,330 --> 00:40:29,170
Come in

616
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,420
Sorry for the wait.

617
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:31,500
Come

618
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:34,380
Hurry up

619
00:40:35,830 --> 00:40:37,540
Chop-chop

620
00:40:40,040 --> 00:40:41,540
Greet

621
00:40:41,540 --> 00:40:43,880
Hello, beautiful

622
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:44,960
Jessica

623
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,540
These are our staff

624
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:48,000
No need to introduce them.

625
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,170
How are their figures?

626
00:41:05,830 --> 00:41:07,080
Good

627
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:09,000
I'll take this one,

628
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:10,580
this one, this one and this one

629
00:41:10,580 --> 00:41:12,630
plus the ones I picked earlier.

630
00:41:12,630 --> 00:41:14,580
Bring them to the main hall

631
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:16,250
I'm going party tonight.

632
00:41:17,210 --> 00:41:18,670
Yes

633
00:41:22,210 --> 00:41:24,000
All right, let's get moving!

634
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,920
Jessica

635
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:27,920
has booked the whole place tonight.

636
00:41:27,920 --> 00:41:29,790
Give it your best,

637
00:41:29,790 --> 00:41:31,380
serve her well.

638
00:41:34,540 --> 00:41:37,500
Just dodge the drinks as usual, okay?

639
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:47,750
Come on, let's drink

640
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,290
It's been a while…

641
00:42:00,040 --> 00:42:01,540
I'll come back for you later.

642
00:42:02,790 --> 00:42:03,830
Hey...

643
00:42:03,830 --> 00:42:05,290
Come on, have a drink.

644
00:42:05,290 --> 00:42:06,750
Thanks everyone for coming.

645
00:42:10,540 --> 00:42:11,710
Just have a little,

646
00:42:11,710 --> 00:42:14,000
it'll help you relax.

647
00:42:14,830 --> 00:42:17,080
I'm not much of a drinker.

648
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:18,790
Then I'll get you some orange juice.

649
00:42:19,460 --> 00:42:20,630
Thank you.

650
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:25,920
Orange juice, please.

651
00:42:48,040 --> 00:42:49,500
Here you go.

652
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:51,500
Thanks

653
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:56,580
Come on, keep me company

654
00:42:56,580 --> 00:42:57,630
Let's go.

655
00:42:59,420 --> 00:43:00,460
Hey, Wei

656
00:43:00,460 --> 00:43:02,000
Jessica

657
00:43:02,000 --> 00:43:03,420
Come, have a seat.

658
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,920
Daniel, come here.

659
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:20,290
Have fun.

660
00:43:24,420 --> 00:43:26,040
It's okay.

661
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:27,790
You look hot…

662
00:43:27,790 --> 00:43:29,420
Let me take your jacket off.

663
00:43:29,420 --> 00:43:30,790
Take a deep breath.

664
00:43:32,630 --> 00:43:33,880
Come on

665
00:43:35,210 --> 00:43:36,420
Let me help you.

666
00:43:36,420 --> 00:43:37,830
Careful now.

